location.fullValue: The 2038 with a 2 car Garage Plan, Laurel Woods

data.description: This beautiful freshly paint home is perfect for those looking for plenty of living space and outdoor enjoyment. The main living area features a fireplace and a kitchen with a center island, nice backsplash, and plenty of storage options. For even more flexibility, there are additional rooms that can be used for whatever you need. The primary bathroom is a dream come true with a separate tub and shower, double sinks, and good under-sink storage. The backyard is fenced in and has a covered sitting area so you can enjoy the outdoors rain or shine. This home has it all and is ready to be your next home. Come take a look and make it yours today! This home has been virtually staged to illustrate its potential.
